00:03:48.140 --> 00:03:49.220
He's got lots of jokes.

00:03:49.220 --> 00:03:50.990
He wants to go on adventures.

00:03:50.990 --> 00:03:53.450
And then you've got Bilbo
Baggins, who's a hobbit.

00:03:53.450 --> 00:03:58.026
